<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Any applications must installable on existing systems and have only one database for use.
So this applications have to use &amp; create uniqe table names.</p>

<p>I think it is useful to set table prefix on createing the db adapter und the select object can complete the given table names with the prefix</p>

<p>e.g.</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$params = array('tprefix'=&gt;'tprefix_', ... );
$db = new Zend_Db('pdo_mysql', $params);
$select = $db-&gt;select();
$select-&gt;from('table', '*');
echo $select-&gt;__toString();
// SELECT * FROM `tprefix_table`
</code></pre>

